Package: cellPCT
Type: Package
Title: Multiple visualization of cell type rate using single cell data
Version: 0.2.1
Author: Evan Xiong
Maintainer: Evan Xiong <yifan.xiong@dynamic-biosystems.com>
Description: Using single cell data in rds format to plot multiple cell type ratio. 
    Five visulization plots included: circle plot, donut plot, sankey plot, 
    stackbar plot, stackline plot.
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Depends: R (>= 4.2.0)
Imports: ggplot2, dplyr, ggalluvial, forcats, SeuratObject, cols4all, treemapify, ggradar, circlize, ComplexHeatmap, grid, gridBase
